narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: After two semesters, I now have rudimentary ability to read the Hebrew Bible.
Biblical hebrew parsing of verbs Reading comprehension improved You get more comfortable with biblical hebrew reading Experience with the use of lexicons and grammars
I learned how to apply the vocabulary and grammar rules I learned to reading and translating text.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: It lacks a personal touch sometimes. You lose the sense that you are dealing with a living text.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: When you sign up for Elementary Biblical Hebrew 1 you are committed to this class. Unfortunately, you cannot shop this class and are stuck with whatever instructor you get.
Take for basic intro to biblical hebrew.
